Zydis bundled source metadata
============================

The files under amalgamated-dist are generated with `assets/amalgamate.py`
from the Zydis git repository (5.0.0 development snapshot):

https://github.com/zyantific/zydis
commit 1167ac17698bbce0d41163e6b61b8a9d9bd67e40 (2026-07-21)
bundled zycore: 75a36c45ae1ad382b0f4e0ede0af84c11ee69928 (v1.5.2-7)

To regenerate them, clone the repository recursively at that commit and run
`python3 assets/amalgamate.py`, then copy the amalgamated-dist files here.

